Her deutam bhoxen xoktichyai rupachi kolpona kelea. Samrtheachem protik oso ximv hem tichem vahon asa. Ti choturbhuz, oxttoxuz, doxbhuz, oxttadoxobhuz asa. Tichea hatamni trixull, khoddg, khettok, porxu oxim xostram asat. Tichea koplacher tisro dollo asa. Tika chonddi, chamundda, bhoirvi, katyaini, kouxiki, tripura, lolita, xrividha, kamarnnea, minakxi, bhognoti oxim namvam asat. Dor eka namva rupachem ek khaxeloponn asun tache fattlean kitem-i tori kotha asa.

