Xoktichim tin mukhel rupam: mull ji adha xokti va mohamaya tika durga mhonnttat. He durgenuch fuddem devo karea khatir ani monxache udrogoti khatir prosonga promann tin rupam ghetlim. Mohasorsvoti him tin rupam trigunnatmok asat. Mohakali hi tomogunni asun ti teach gunnanchea rudroxivakodde sombond asa. Mohalkxmi hi sotvogunni asun ti zogdomba asa ani sotvogunni vixnnukodde sombond asa.Tika hi videadayi deuta asa. Hea tinuy rupancheo utpotikotha markonddey purannantlea soptoxotint dileat. Tancho apros oso asa-

1)mohakali: proloi kallant vixnnu yognidrent xexoxyyecher nhidil'lo astona, tachea kanantlean modhu ani koittobh namvache don doity bhair sorle. Poilinch tankam bromha dislo. Te borobor te taka marpak dhamvle. Bromhean bhogvontache yognidrechi tokhnnai korun tika sanglem, tum hea osurank bhuloi ani tea vixnnuk zago kor. Tem aikotach vixnnuchea angantlean mohakali utpon'n zali ani vixnnu zago zalo. Uprant vixnnu ani tea doiteanchem zhuz pettlem. Mahakalin tea doiteank veustit bhuloile ani tankam budhdibhrom' zalo. Tamnni vixnnuk sanglem, tum boro zhuz khelltta ami tujer prosn'n zaleat, tuka zai to vor mag. Tacher vixnnun aplea hatamnich tankam moronn yeuchem oso vor maglo. Doiteamni vixnnuk zai toso vor dilo punn ek ott ghatli, je suvatir udok aschemna oxach zagear vixnnun tankam marchem karonn tea vellar proloi zal'lean sogli prithvi ugkan bhoril'li. Vixnnun tanchi ott many keli ani aple manddyer tancheo tokleo gheun kapun uddoileo. Oxe toren mohakalin modhu-koittbhanche budhdik oso bhrom' kelo

2)mohalkxmi: mohixasur namvacho doity mohaboli zalo ani tannem devam kodde zhuz suru kelem indrak haroun to svota devancho raza zalo uprant soglle devo bromhodevak gheun vixnnu ani xonkra mhoreant gele ani tankam hi khobor sangli. Te borobor vixnnu, xonkrasoit sogllea devanchea angantlean ek tejixtt oso zhot bhair ailo ani tatuntlean mohalkxmi hi devi utpon'n zali. Devamni apapolim xostram tika divn mohixasuracho vodh korpak sanglem. Tinnem ek vhodd gorzona korini fuddem mohixasur ailo. Tannem mohalkxmi kodde vhodd zhuz kelem. Punn mohalkxmin tacho vodh korun devank obhoi dilem

